{
  "id": "RAW_0fc6e73e",
  "title": "腾讯的社交实验：当 AI 混进人类「群聊」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTMwNDMwODQ0MQ==&mid=2653097797&idx=1&sn=ff096b76437423b763dd2435a029926f",
  "date": "2026-01-26 09:49:00",
  "author": "极客公园",
  "siteName": "极客公园",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\" data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;margin-bottom:0em;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7919254658385093\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"644\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;vertical-align:bottom;width:100%;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8cu01Kavc5a1beeFZJwH0ia2zQxvQL8lxlOxxnvypMFmUfem6u5m6rueyEGtQb9HTLBPaNAnDmUKeh9zricd17lA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"644.0035746201966\" data-cropy1=\"158.99910634495083\" data-cropy2=\"668.0250223413761\" data-backw=\"289\" data-backh=\"229\" data-imgfileid=\"505614132\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=56d8aa18&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5a1beeFZJwH0ia2zQxvQL8lxEEzJmtw9aNl7qmYs3vicDU9150ouWOSxVkJxl8uj4JZ7keArdJEcZeg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:25px 18px 18px;margin:-0.6em 8px 2em;background-size:100%;letter-spacing:0.3px;clear:both;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8em;background-position:100% 100%;background-color:rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;background-repeat:no-repeat;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj8uu\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">元宝派，会迎来下一个春晚红包时刻吗？</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;margin-top:25px;min-height:1em;line-height:normal;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj919tb\"><span leaf=\"\">作者｜连冉</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;line-height:normal;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9ym6\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑｜</span><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">郑玄</span></strong></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj91vtu\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">1 月 26 日，腾讯旗下 AI 助手元宝开启了社交 AI 玩法「元宝派」内测。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9rif\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">极客公园第一时间上手体验：用户可以选择创建一个「派」，或者加入一个已有的「派」。用户可以在派内 @ 元宝或引用元宝的话，让元宝 AI 总结派内聊天、创建健身、阅读等兴趣打卡活动，由元宝 AI 担任「监督员」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj921re\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">除了文字聊天，用户也可以在派内进行「图片二创」，将一张普通的照片变成有趣的「梗图」或表情包。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9xux\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">看着群聊里不停跳出新消息，元宝也是尽量花样百出地跟群友互动，虽然目前不知道这种热闹是否可持续，但有一个 AI 在群里，这个群确实再也不怕冷场了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"4590\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4ae8033b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5a1beeFZJwH0ia2zQxvQL8lxyRtpcADI2MTrRQhj2SYnJwEzanCLRrNf2YD43Q6WeIjVFu4cz80Ajw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9vq0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9pyj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">据了解，元宝派后续公测还将开放上线「一起看」、「一起听」玩法，该玩法接⼊了腾讯会议的⾳视频底层能⼒，让⽤户可以邀请派内好友同步观看一部电影、一场比赛、听一首歌。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj95as\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这次更新在功能上新之余，也是一次对 AI 应用「生存形态」的重新思考：当 AI 不再只是工具，而是社交关系中的「连接器」时，会发生什么变化？</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkuwxn171ns5\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9t1x\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></em></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj91qen\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"font-size:17px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-is-content=\"t\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从「对着 AI 提问」到</span></strong></span></strong></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9fmq\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"font-size:17px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-is-content=\"t\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「和 AI 一起生活」</span></strong></span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj93kd\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">我创建了「AI 大派」，一开始，群里有点冷清，随着加入群聊的朋友越来越多，「AI 大派」也变得热闹起来，群友从「炒作公司」的创业剧本，一路聊到哲学和宇宙学，以及 AI 的边界，甚至还有东西方文明发展路径的差异，佛教怎么看待现实，可以说是天南海北，脑洞大开。元宝在里面也是不会让任何一句话掉在地上，回答还时不时有点小幽默、小自恋。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.16793893129771\" data-w=\"1179\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"1253\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=02be529a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5a1beeFZJwH0ia2zQxvQL8lxL1IwdU1nPzzssyOLYHCVRkCBToU4ibBrMdpk3qqS4ma0fsv4L0HROkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9lmo\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj953w\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">「元宝派」的产品逻辑并不复杂，但它尝试解决一个核心痛点：AI 使用场景的孤岛化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj91vr0\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在内测版本中，可以看到腾讯正试图打通其最核心的护城河——社交关系链。用户可以将「派号」或邀请链接直接分享给微信、QQ 好友，实现一键入群。这一步看似简单，实则极大地降低了用户把 AI 引入生活圈的门槛。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"4590\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=686ba1b4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5a1beeFZJwH0ia2zQxvQL8lx6IxrFkxPic0kdDhIxYDIPic6loMbCxMKOJM9s8hc5WHicne25mIrbdibsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9zy6\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9vkh\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">如果只看表面，元宝派很容易被误解为「AI 版的 QQ 群」或者「AI 版的 discord」。但真正有意思的地方，在于它对 AI 角色的重新设计。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj923f3\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在以往的协作软件（如飞书、钉钉）里，AI 往往是一个效率插件。但在元宝派里，AI 更像是一个「默认参与者」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj921bi\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">它不仅仅是被动等待指令。当你和朋友讨论电影剧情时，它可以被随时 @ 出来补充背景；当你发了一张生活照，它能主动参与二创；当你需要共同学习时，它又变成了领读员。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj910q\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">作为「气氛组」，以前我们用 AI 生成图是自己看，现在「元宝派」支持图片趣味二创。发一张照片，AI 能把它变成梗图或表情包。这种基于多模态能力的「玩梗」，本质上是在降低社交互动的摩擦力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.16793893129771\" data-w=\"1179\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"1253\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ab97082a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5a1beeFZJwH0ia2zQxvQL8lxpFfz9x6HRyovyrAyleyeZ4CKWcve9mH8Dk1SwEZknFUkASPzTX56YQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9r79\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9zyi\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">作为「全能助理」，它保留了工具属性。可以在群里 @ 元宝，让它总结杂乱的聊天记录，或者制定一个背单词、健身的打卡计划，也可以设置提醒。在一个学习小组或兴趣群里，AI 也能够扮演一个不知疲倦的「监督员」角色。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"4590\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fbe6e90a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5a1beeFZJwH0ia2zQxvQL8lxBbXVyfNKKOtqvY6hI1hW4f2PamhPiaib28pQCCyagmROBnCR7d5dbymA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9y7i\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9xs4\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这种设计思路的转变，可以看到腾讯试图将 AI 从「人机交互」推向「人机共生」——从一个搜索框或者对话框，走向一个能感知上下文、能接梗、能干活的「硅基群友」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9ldn\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">同时，腾讯在「元宝派」中通过技术复用，构建了一些差异化的体验。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj91wkx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">除了常规的文本对话，元宝派接入了腾讯会议的底层音视频能力，支持「共享屏幕」和未来的「一起看」、「一起听」功能。这意味着，这个「派」还将成为一个虚拟的线上客厅。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj97vx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">想象一下这个场景：你和异地的朋友在「派」里同步观看一部电影，或者通过屏幕共享一起研究游戏攻略，遇到不懂的剧情或关卡，随时 @ 元宝 进行提问。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9f51\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这或许是一种「场景+技术」的降维打击。大多数创业公司的 AI 社交产品往往受限于基础设施，难以提供低延迟、高质量的同步视听体验。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj91slb\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">而腾讯直接调用了内部成熟的会议组件，让 AI 社交从纯文本/语音交互，升级到了实时互动的多媒体交互。这不仅丰富了群聊的维度，也为 AI 介入人类社交提供了更自然的切口——不是为了用 AI 而用 AI，而是在共同娱乐中自然地使用 AI。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkux6p4w4ur\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj921eg\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></em></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj914c9\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"font-size:17px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-is-content=\"t\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">腾讯在试探 AI 的下一个入口形态</span></strong></span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9135p\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">如果把视角拉高，元宝派更像是腾讯在做的一次方向性试验。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9673\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">过去十多年，腾讯最强的能力始终是「场」——从 QQ 群、微信群，到各种兴趣群、学习群、项目群，它擅长的不是工具本身，而是把人聚在一起。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj912gb\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">而 AI 时代的问题是：AI 应该站在「人和人之间」的哪个位置？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj91an3\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">元宝派给出的答案是： 不是站在对话框里，也不是站在搜索入口，而是站在「人正在一起做事的地方」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9tba\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">为了推动这个形态的普及，腾讯甚至宣布将在春节期间投入 10 亿现金红包。这在近年来的互联网营销中已不多见，用真金白银结合强社交裂变，元宝尝试快速推动用户完成从「单机 AI」到「社交 AI」的习惯迁移。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj916pd\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">在今天的腾讯年会上，腾讯董事会主席马化腾提到元宝春节分 10 亿元现金活动时称，希望重现当年微信红包的盛况。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj920b8\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">马化腾也提到了元宝在做的社交类产品元宝派，称其本来是绝密的项目，他还在大会现场为元宝「拉票」，安利大家下载体验。「再预告一下，因为我自己也在内测，我们的元宝也会引入一个新的和我们特点结合的社交功能。元宝派未来可能还会再设计一些通信的功能，我们先结合自己的优势，社交通信以及我们的关系链营造一个好的氛围。」</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"952\" data-backw=\"578\" data-ratio=\"1.6463104325699744\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-w=\"1179\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=25ab2d52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5a1beeFZJwH0ia2zQxvQL8lxeNEVZ1a4uFDmMr0mroHWbeicq4DhtAOCxqXsneRbaGswX8eItgkm1kA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9p81\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">图片来源：元宝公众号</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9wfx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">10 年前的 2015 年春晚，腾讯曾通过微信「摇一摇」发放 5 亿现金红包，除夕当晚参与用户达 2000 万，红包收发总量超 10 亿个，峰值互动次数达每分钟 8.1 亿次，由此推动微信支付的影响力显著增强。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj9bha\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">当然，多人场景下的 AI 交互（如插话时机、隐私边界）依然面临挑战。从这个角度看，它真正验证的不是某一个功能，而是一个更大的命题：当 AI 能长期存在于一个真实社交空间里，它是否会自然变成一种新的基础设施？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj91iab\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">如果这个命题成立，那么未来的 AI 产品形态，可能不再是「超级助手」，而是无数个嵌入具体场景的、低存在感但高参与度的 AI 角色。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj95jn\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">元宝派未必是答案，但它至少说明了一件事：在 AI 走向「陪伴」和「共创」的路上，腾讯依然选择从社交这条老路，开一条新支线。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkuzaqj99ea\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这或许才是它更值得被关注的地方。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "腾讯推出社交 AI 玩法「元宝派」，尝试将 AI 从单一工具转化为嵌入社交关系链的“硅基群友”，探索人机共生的新入口。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "腾讯推出社交 AI 玩法「元宝派」，尝试将 AI 从单一工具转化为嵌入社交关系链的“硅基群友”，探索人机共生的新入口。",
  "summary": "本文详细介绍了腾讯旗下 AI 助手元宝新推出的内测功能「元宝派」。该产品通过打通微信、QQ 的社交关系链，允许用户创建包含 AI 的群聊空间。在「派」中，AI 不再仅是问答工具，而是作为“默认参与者”承担气氛组、图片二创、聊天总结及兴趣打卡监督员等角色。文章指出，腾讯利用其音视频底层能力（如共享屏幕、一起看/听）构建差异化体验，试图将 AI 从“人机交互”推向“人机共生”。马化腾对此项目寄予厚望，希望通过春节 10 亿红包活动重现微信红包的社交裂变奇迹，验证 AI 作为社交基础设施的新形态。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
